@startuml seq-17-admin-product
' 序列图17：管理员上架商品
title 管理员上架商品序列图

actor 管理员 as Admin
participant "admin-edit.js" as Front
participant "AdminController" as Ctrl
participant "ProductService" as Svc
participant "ProductMapper" as Mapper
database "MySQL" as DB

Admin -> Front: 填写商品名/价格/图片/分类/库存
Admin -> Front: 点击"上架"
Front -> Ctrl: POST /api/admin/product/add(name,price,image,categoryId,stock)
Ctrl -> Svc: add(product)
Svc -> Mapper: insert(product)
Mapper -> DB: INSERT INTO product
DB --> Mapper: product_id
Mapper --> Svc: product_id
Svc --> Ctrl: product_id
Ctrl --> Front: {code:200}
Front --> Admin: 提示上架成功,返回管理列表

@enduml
